text: Discover this 4-bedroom farmhouse set on 33 picturesque acres, offering a perfect blend of pasture and parklike grounds. Nestled on a quiet road with stunning Mt. Baker views, this property boasts a large hip roof barn and a versatile layout with a primary bedroom on the main floor. The partially wooded landscape provides privacy and tranquility, making it an ideal retreat. With its expansive acreage and potential for division, this property is ripe with possibilities. Embrace country living in this serene, private setting. Dont miss out on this unique opportunity!

Recently updated 3 bedroom plus an office room home with lots of off-street parking. New kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and luxury vinyl plank throughout the home. Partial fence around the home. Spacious shed in the back for storage. As well as the corner of the property with mature trees . SandyPoint amenities include: pool, golf, marina, tennis, playground and clubhouse. Seller is offering $10k for closing costs and the sewer assessment has been paid off in full!

Welcome to your idyllic home tucked on the end of Clipper Rd. The main home has two bedrooms, a loft, a sunroom and a detached carport. Bask in the beautiful mountain views from the large deck, perfect for entertaining guests. A short drive down the road leads you to a quaint cabin that sits on a lower, large plot surrounded by garden space and across from a spacious shop for all your toys. The one bedroom cabin offers the second wood stove, and is perfect for guests, or a private studio. Opportunity to rent the cabin long term or potential short term rentals. A washer and dryer is located in the shop. Enjoy 6 acres enveloped by firs, cedars and mature landscaping. This property offers privacy and tranquility while overlooking the valley.

Great opportunity to own this completely updated charming home. Spacious bright kitchen with lots cabinets for storage, large living room, new double pane windows, new flooring, new paint, new Led lighting, new decks, move in ready. All new appliances all include. Extra parking space, storage shed included. Located in a close distance to town amenities, grocery stores and downtown. Buyer must be approved by the park before closing. This is a Must see!!

Brand NEW Marlette home at Ponderosa Estates! Affordability and a gorgeous location minutes from Birch Bay! Appealing 23 acre park with a very northwest vibe. This new 3 bed, 2 bath home features a primary en-suite with spacious walk-in closet, dual sinks and ample storage. Bright contemporary kitchen with large pantry, gorgeous countertops with tile back splash and brand new stainless steel appliances. A spacious backyard where you can create your own garden and patio area. Watch the sunrise from your beautiful covered front porch. Take a walk down to the beach and enjoy cafes, restaurants, parks, trails and spectacular sunsets on the promenade. An all age year-round community.

Turn key, charming ground-level condo with Mt. Baker Views! Welcome to this spacious and wall-maintained 2-bed 1-bath condo, perfectly positioned on the ground floor with no stairs for easy access. The large windows flood the home with natural light, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. Featuring a stunning Mt. Baker view from the back patio. Newer carpet and paint throughout. Enjoy the breathtaking sunrise views and the calming breeze from the patio. Convenient covered carport and storage directly in front of the front door. Private front patio deck and back patio space. Excellent location in the active and accessible community of Ferndale, just minutes from downtown!

This home is located in Fairhaven's Parkway Village 55 and better active community. If you have been looking for a community to connect w/ and experience all that South Bellingham has to offer, this is it! Come look at this 3 bdrm, 2 bthrm single-level home w/ an attached carport and storage area. You will enjoy the south-facing sunny deck or the covered patio located just off the dining room. The kitchen is light and bright w/a skylight, updated kitchen cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The home has been well taken care of w/ lots of significant updates like a newer furnace and A/C system, new windows, and a new water heater (a complete list is available). There are established garden beds and a fully fenced backyard space to enjoy.

Welcome home to your single level, immaculately maintained, 3 bed 2 ba home with a flat driveway just inside Gate 3. Updated throughout with an eye for detail & modern aesthetic that you'll appreciate. Open layout for socializing in the newly renovated kitchen complete with modern cabinetry + incredible storage, quartz countertops, deep stainless sink & penny tile backsplash. New roof and all five skylights in 2022 + range in 2023. High eff. furnace + Heat pump & A/C, hardie siding, solid floors & white paint throughout. Great room style layout opens to trex deck over looking a gated sunny garden space. Generous and bright primary bed w/ ensuite double sink bath + 2 closets & private access to the deck. Tall crawl space for endless storage!

Presale. Make your color and upgrade selections. Salt water & sea breezes greet you! Cypress, offered in the new gated community Woodberry, at Semiahmoo. 2690 sq ft. The main level lives like a one level home with Primary, office, dining room, open floor plan, kitchen and living with 1.5 baths, enjoy 2 bedrooms, bath and loft area upstairs. Quality finishes, flooring, quartz, soft close cabinets, stainless appliances, mini split heating / Quality limited life time roof, patio & more. 25 minutes from Costco. 10 minutes from border. Area amenities are ala carte and include Golf & CC, Marina, waterfront park, 200 room Inn at Semiahmoo, Spa, Tennis club, walking trails kayaking, biking. 3 Car gar. Brokers registration policy #4908

One of the best priced homes in Whatcom County! Cozy 1 bedroom cottage on a quiet cul de sac. Home will require some TLC but has great potential and room for your finishing touches. Private lot with shop space and shed for storage. Embrace rustic tranquility out in Maple Falls!

Experience luxurious living in this beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bath condo nestled within Raspberry Ridge Golf Course neighborhood. This home has an attached garage, with plenty of storage space and a work bench, and a newer heating and cooling unit. Wake up to peek a boo views of Mt. Baker at this turn key end unit condo. As an end unit, this property offers enhanced privacy and abundant natural light. The spacious, single-level layout provides effortless comfort and accessibility, perfect for a low-maintenance lifestyle, as the HOA covers all the lawn care. This home offers a perfect blend of relaxation and recreation.

Captivating bay & island views from this 2016-built Samish Hill craftsman. Originally constructed as a builder's own home, you'll notice exceptional workmanship and extra bells & whistles throughout. Open concept layout on the main level with an entertainer's kitchen showcasing a leathered quartzite island, soft-close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and tile backsplash. Also on the main level is a bedroom/office with a 3/4 bathroom across the hall. Upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms with vaulted ceilings. On the lower level, a 675 SQFT bonus room with wet bar. An oversized 2-car garage allows space for storage or a workshop. The trail behind the home provides quick access to Lake Padden.

Sweet Happy Valley location, close to Fairhaven, schools, parks and the 100 Acre Woods Trails. Two-bedroom rambler on a large level lot offers a lot of potential for the right buyer. Three-quarter bath was remodeled for handicap access. Stairs lead to additional square footage with lower ceiling height (appx 5'10 ) for storage which is not included in the appx. square feet. Definitely a cosmetic fixer, but the home is well placed for additional development. Gas forced air heat, all appliances included, large utility room & 1 car carport. Close to Western Washington State University!

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Showings available between 12-3pm, 7dys a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

An easy simple downsize for anyone seeking quiet refuge & more time to do things that matter. Welcome home to a kinder, more carefree way to live. Ideal for nature lovers & golf enthusiasts. Perfectly situated--south-facing sunshine all day! Great design with vaulted ceilings & wonderful windows. This spaciously gracious home offers top-of-the-line finishes, gas fireplace, stainless appliances, excellent exterior decks & lots of storage. Walking distance to all amenities-a best value property!

Welcome home to the Crown Jewel of Galbraith! This is a once in a lifetime opportunity to own one of the best properties Bellingham has to offer. Perfectly appointed with incredible privacy, your own private pond, and a large shop for all your toys equipped with its own bath and plumbed for shower addition, fireplace, huge solar panel array and loft area. Enjoy gorgeous views from anywhere inside or outside no matter what time of the year. Less than a one minute ride to Galbraith, this is a mountain biker's dream. Near Lake Padden and within short driving distance to Fairhaven and downtown Bellingham. Thoughtfully designed to create up to 2 MIL suites or ADUs within the existing home, with minimal effort. This property has it all!

This home sits on a gently sloped hillside with wonderful views of Birch Bay and Mt. Baker. Good sized corner lot with open views from almost every room. Spacious 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath, 200 Sf enclosed porch and 400 SF attached garage. 1974 manufactured home is in good condition. Ready to move in or to rented out. HOA dues are only $25/year. Very quite and friendly community. Listing agent is related to the Seller.

Relax, renew, refresh at the Tides! This single-level home represents Birch Bay living at its finest. Close to the beach, restaurants, breweries and other amenities. Enjoy morning coffee in the sun on your front patio, gas fireplace to cozy up next to with a cup of cocoa in the cooler months, private driveway, open concept living with vaulted ceilings, custom shelving modifications, in-unit washer/dryer. This home is uniquely configured with no shared living space walls for maximum privacy. The Tides community provides ample parking, bay views, private storage, gas stub for BBQ, pool & hot tub access, clubhouse with kitchen, and game room. Enjoy relaxing walks to the beach and exploring the local C Shop.

Extraordinary brand new 3 bed, 2.75 bath custom-built home nestled on a sunny cul-de-sac lot, boasting mountain views. This home is designed for seamless entertaining with tons of extras, featuring a great open floor plan, vaulted wood ceiling, open stairway & a cozy wood-burning fireplace, metal roof & AC. The main floor offers spa like primary suite and second bedroom. Step outside to discover an oversized deck & luxurious hot tub, perfect for relaxation & gatherings. This property presents an opportunity to own a stunning glacier retreat near Mt. Baker & Nooksack River. Residents enjoy access to a clubhouse, tennis courts, play ground, river, pool, sauna & more. Experience the best of mountain living in this remarkable home.

This home is privately situated on a dead-end lane along the sought-after Lake Whatcom waterfront. This idyllic, quaint home is set back from the street along an enchanting winding path amongst lush, mature landscaping. The freshly painted home is in a cleared sunny area with a covered patio and garden shed beside the front entry. Inside, there are formal and informal dining and living rooms, along with a bar and absolutely stunning lake and mountain views. The kitchen is in the center of the main floor making this the absolutely perfect home for entertaining! Upstairs is the primary suite and a 2nd bed (currently an office). There's a large yard toward the lake with 50' of waterfront, a shared dock, fire pit patiomand kayak storage.

Charming quintessential Cedar Pan Abode cabin privately nestled amongst nature with beautiful peek-a-boo ocean views. This property is tucked in at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac on a third of an acre with eastern exposure. The sale includes a second lot that offers complete privacy to the cabin. Open layout with vaulted ceilings throughout, featuring 3 beds + 1 bath with a wood stove in the heart of the cabin. Endless charm, and large windows to take in the ocean vistas or views of the gardens featuring beautiful evergreen trees. Detached garage with space for a workshop. Don't miss out on this peaceful retreat close to the beaches in beautiful Point Roberts.

Come home to breathtaking Bay views and spectacular sunsets every evening! This beautifully maintained property offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms + 3/4 bath downstairs, updated kitchen and a new roof. Step into your own oasis with a fenced backyard ideal for privacy and a large back deck perfect for entertaining or relaxing in peace. Whether you enjoy hosting gatherings or simply unwinding outdoors, this home provides the perfect setting. The vaulted ceilings and large picture windows fill the home with light and warmth. Upstairs don't miss the private balcony off the spacious primary suite. Perched at the top of Woodside on Barkley Hill, you're just minutes to the expansive trail system and all the amenities in Barkley Village.

Classic 1966 rambler on a large lot perfectly located deep on quiet cul-de-sac near the top of one of Bellingham's most sought after neighborhoods. This Toledo hill beauty is 2790 sf , 4 bd. 3 baths on 14, 824 sf lot. This is a home entertainers gold mine. 1/2 the back yard is inground pool w/hot tub surrounded by huge patio w/ fireplace bbq area all fenced in for safety and the other half is wide open for your playground / garden / lawn / imagination. All this is totally private and screened by landscaping and fence. You'll always be excited to get home to this private oasis in the heart of fantastic Bellingham. Literally minutes from everywhere you want to be and easy access to major thru roads and I-5.

One level Lynden Living at its finest in this 55 and older community! 3 Bedrooms with an option to have an office or an additional fourth bedroom. Radiant floor heat with A/C and central vac system. Huge primary bedroom with his and hers walk in closets, sinks, and a tiled walk-in shower. Kitchen features slab granite with stainless steel appliances. There is also an oversized garage with a workshop area. The property is nicely landscaped with a covered patio, hot tub & sprinkler system, the back yard is fenced for privacy.

You won't want to miss this newly remodeled home located on a quiet private drive. Sitting on an almost 3/4 acre lot, this charming home features new flooring, cabinets, countertops, tile backsplash and SS appliances. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms, including two primary bedrooms with attached baths and a large living room with tons of natural light. The dining room is connected to the large, open kitchen and leads out to the sizeable backyard! Complete with a two car garage and wonderful new landscaping. Plenty of room for shop and/or ADU and dividable in the future. Call today to schedule your showing!

Explore this vacation get away, well-kept park model located in the sought-after beachfront community of Leisure Park. This unit stands as the most economical vacation option in Birch Bay, boasting an ideal location, comprehensive amenities, and affordability. The tranquil neighborhood offers a clubhouse, tennis courts, a playground, and an outdoor swimming pool. The park model is fully furnished, featuring a Hida bed sofa for guests, double bunk beds, a carpeted covered deck, and a storage shed, all facing west to capture abundant sunlight and breathtaking sunrise vistas. A professional HOA with board members dedicated to the community enhances the living experience. Note that this is exclusively a 180-day park.

Imagine living across the beach at an incredibly affordable price! This very comfortable park model is the largest in the community with 786sf and 350sf of covered deck space. Built in 2014, this unit has 2 bedrooms & 1 bathroom with walk-in shower. Lots of natural light, double pane windows, ceiling fan & beautiful flooring. Open kitchen concept with nice appliances and a new washer & dryer. Enjoy the generous deck for morning coffee or BBQ's with friends. Lots of storage space with 2 extra sheds. Stroll across the street for a beach bonfire while watching the sunset. Live in the heart of Birch Bay with dining, shops, and entertainment. Did I mention it's fully furnished? Grab your kayak, toothbrush & towel. Lots of fun, this is the one!

The perfect multifamily investment in growing and appreciating Blaine WA. Walking distance to Canadian border. Incredible income potential in 1 bed and 2 bed single level units with decks. Remodeled interiors are lovely. Large 11, 000 sf lot allows for so much flexibility for the future. 1, 400+ sf heated shop split into 4 separate rentable areas would make great storage for renters, additional income, and/or owner use. Rents are increasing in Blaine! This is a rare opportunity as a high income rental, partial owner occupy, or extended living residence with separate living areas. Address is actually 410 and 420 5th Street. Seller has assumable loan at low APR.

LUXURY BEACHFRONT LIVING on the pristine shores of the desirable & sought after Lake Samish! This BRAND NEW custom built 2, 470 square foot contemporary home exudes meticulous craftsmanship with a sharp and flowing open design. Experience the best of lake living with dusk to dawn sun, picturesque sunsets, private dock & designer landscaping. Enjoy the sound & serenity of the lake with walls of folding glass leading to multiple patios to enjoy your evenings while dining al fresco. Additional features include, luxurious primary suite & bath with balcony, great room/dining room opening to a chefs kitchen, large bonus room with bathroom that is accessed by a glass bridge, and a 3 car garage. The perfect mix of lakeside charm and MODERN LUXURY!

Here is a great starter property in Div. 2 at The Glen at Maple Falls. Property has greenbelt on one side and the entire back of property. It has a 1978 Nomad travel trailer that is nice and dry on the inside. Trailer needs some minor plumbing repairs, but is in good shape for its age, thanks to the auxiliary roof covering it. Trailer and lot sold as is. Septic just inspected and passed. The Glen has 2 pools, hot tub, sauna, 2 clubhouses, playgrounds, trails, tennis courts, disc golf course, laundry facilities, 24/7 security with gated entrance, and so much more! Zoned rec for 120 days use per yr.

HOT PRICED 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Craftsman charmer in the popular Bay Crest neighborhood featuring downstairs open concept kitchen/ dining & two living room layout with gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans and laundry room.Upstairs features 2 spacious bedrooms that share a full bathroom & a roomy primary with walk-in closet, really nice en suite with dual sink vanity, separate shower & jetted tub! Fully fenced back yard for play & pets, nice long covered front porch for the rainy days looking out over a nice front yard & a two car garage. All located minutes from the beaches, Birch Bay Park, & all the fun Birch Bay has to offer, close to I-5 for quick run to Canada or Bellingham. Priced aggressively to cover new flooring

Embrace the ultimate blend of tranquility and adventure with this exceptional vacant level lot, ready for your dream home! Located in a quiet dead-end cul-de-sac, this ready-to-build lot ensures privacy and minimal traffic, with essential utilities at the street and already partially fenced. There's an opportunity to purchase the adjacent lot for a larger property, creating an expansive estate.45 minute Scenic drive to Mt. Baker Ski Resort for skiing, snowboarding and fun in the snow or 45 minute drive to the bay. You are minutes from Canada, and easy access to fishing, hiking, hunting, and more. This lot is the foundation for a lifestyle filled with adventure and relaxation. Parcel next to it is also available for sale.

Discover this lovely single-story craftsman home in the Maple Ridge community. Upon entering, you'll find a spacious living area filled with natural light, ideal for relaxing or entertaining. The kitchen boasts ample counter space and storage, making meal preparation a breeze. The 4th bedroom can easily serve as a home office, study, or guest room. The master suite provides a peaceful retreat with its cozy bedroom, ensuite bathroom, and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom ensure there's plenty of space for everyone. Upstairs, the bonus room above the garage provides a private entertainment area, or extra storage space. Outside, the fully fenced backyard provides privacy and and space for outdoor activities.

Southside beautifully updated ground floor unit with a charming patio in sought after Cypress Condos. New paint, new base trim, new laminate and vinyl plank flooring, new appliances and more. Desirable area near WWU and Fairhaven-close to trail system, bus line and I-5. Kitchen has stainless {new} appliances, Maple cabinets, and vinyl plank flooring. Stackable washer and dryer in unit/closet. Spacious bathroom with storage. Newer hot water tank. Community features: elevator, secured entry, and fitness center. This studio offers an efficient layout, warm PNW finishes, large bathroom, and west-facing patio. Convenient reserved parking space, sought-after location and a rare find at this price.

This 2019 Forest River Park Model is in excellent condition. In Div. 4 at The Glen, this unit is turn-key and ready to move in. Has a full-length deck with skylights to let the natural light come in. Plenty of room for entertaining. This has a double loft and hide-a-bed in the living room for lots of guests. Spacious kitchen, 3/4 bath. Even comes with a backup generator. Has shed in front for storage and a propane clothes dryer. Great for skiing at Baker in winter or hiking in the summer. The Glen has 2 pools, hot tub, sauna, 2 clubhouses, tennis courts, disc golf, laundry facilities, restrooms w/showers, trails, playgrounds, 24/7 security w/gated entrance, and so much more! A must see! Zoned rec. 120 days per year.

This vintage mid-century rambler is a true retro gem on a nearly half acre oasis tucked into the coveted Cornwall Park neighborhood. Perfectly located in a central location near great schools, Cornwall Park, the Rose Garden, trail system, St. Joseph's Hospital & a bustling downtown. The well designed floor plan creates a home that lives much larger than the square footage. The deep garage has workshop space and an old fashioned canning room. The cornucopia of fruit growing in the massive manicured backyard includes cherries blueberries, green gage plums & gravenstein apples. Enjoy this amazing private yard from a cozy covered back patio. Whether you're a lover of retro style or looking to modernize, this home offers endless possibilities.

Amazing condo in the heart of Bellingham, located close to amenities, entertainment, local farmers market, & I-5. This 5th story condo w/elevator access features new floors, light fixtures & paint. Natural light pours through the ample windows in this coveted corner unit. Open kitchen & dining w/newer appliances, cozy fireplace in living room is an excellent heat source for main part of home. Off the dining room is a balcony that gets nice sun during the day + overlooks Depot Market & downtown. Primary BR features reading nook & newly remodeled bath. The extra bedroom/office boasts French doors. This unit has a W/D & plenty of extra storage! Underground parking for your safety. A private, owner access only, common balcony loc. on 2nd floor.
neighborhoods: City Center Bellingham, Downtown District Bellingham

text: Easy living in this low-maintenance, single-story delight in Portal Commons on a cul-de-sac. 3 bedrooms and 2 bath including private primary suite w/walk-in closet and full bath. Warm cherry laminate floors extend thru a large portion of the living space. In the kitchen find a sparkling set of stainless steel appliances and a view out the window and sliding door to a large, level yard that's partially fenced. Just waiting for you to entertain on the patio, plant a garden, you name it! Plenty of room in your 2 car garage for storage, vehicles, or toys. A short drive to Bellingham and less than a minute to be on I5. Close to everything yet tucked away from the hustle & bustle.

Discover unparalleled equestrian living in this stunning Colonial-style home in beautiful Whatcom County. This 3 bdrm, 3.5 bath residence on 14.55 level acres boasts luxurious finishes, hardwood & slate flooring, vaulted ceilings, and a Chef's kitchen. Enjoy cozy evenings by one of the 3 fireplaces, workout in the flex room, or entertain in the spacious living & family rooms. A covered back deck & balcony overlook the cross-fenced pastures. A second parcel has a run-in barn w/tack rm and an outdoor riding arena. It offers a 2 bdrm septic system & potential for a second residence. With its natural beauty & convenient location, this amazing property is perfect for those seeking a peaceful retreat without sacrificing modern amenities.

This property has space to roam! At over 4, 300 square feet and close to a comfort station, this large corner lot is spacious and private feeling. With a 1989 trailer and big covered deck, this property is also perfect for entertaining. Also included is a shed (also with a metal roof) and a fire pit area. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Welcome to your cozy haven in one of Bellingham's premier all ages mobile home parks! This charming 2-bed, 2-bath residence built in 2004 offers not only comfortable living but also the convenience of an office space. Step into an inviting open-concept kitchen, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying everyday meals. The bath off the primary bedroom adds a touch of luxury and privacy. Nestled in a serene and quiet neighborhood, you'll relish peaceful evenings and weekends. Plus, with parks and amenities nearby, every convenience is within reach. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a viewing today!

Adorable beach Home w/ 50 feet of serene waterfront. 2 bedrooms 1.75 baths. Recent complete renovation of the entire home to highlight the views and enhance the interior comfort and elegance. Inviting open concept floor plan engage residents and guests with an open airy connection with the outdoors in any season. Loft master suite with private balcony. Private 2nd bedroom suite, and a flex space for your ideas. Wildlife abounds from the deck with Herons, Seals, Loons, Grey Whales, & Orcas! Stunning views of the Canadian Cascades, Pt Roberts, Mt. Constitution on Orcas & Sandy Point! Abundant raised bed gardens & fruit to enjoy in season. Fee simple, Not Leased Land. VRBO Potential. Mini-Split HVAC. Work/storage building, RV parking.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Amazing opportunity to finally live in the kind of home that checks all the boxes! This architecturally pleasing 3, 628 sqft log home is perfectly situated on almost 14 acres to take advantage of the outstanding sun exposure and views to the west, while maintaining a presence on the property of prominence and stature. With 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, wrap around decks, and two primary suites, this property has the size and elegance to accommodate almost anyone. Featuring a new 40x30 shop Hardwood floors, granite countertops, SS appliances, built-in surround system, radiant heat floors and a Navien Boiler, there is nothing to do but move in. A circular gravel driveway gives multiple access points to the home and allows for one level living!

Welcome to the charming Glenhaven community, nestled along peaceful Cain Lake. This 1372 sqft property offers 2 spacious bedrooms plus an additional den/office. Step inside and discover a bright & airy open living area, complete with a cozy wood stove. Vaulted ceilings and skylights throughout, flooding the space with natural light and inviting ambiance. The newly renovated kitchen features quartz countertops and fresh appliances. Many recent upgrades, including a new furnace, water heater and roof. Oversized 2-car garage + 2nd driveway perfect for Boat/RV parking. Just 1 mile from Lake Whatcom for ALL your boating fun! Exclusive community access to a pool, playground, tennis courts, fishing and more, ideal for creating lasting memories.

Discover a prime 3.2-acre piece of vacant land on Semiahmoo Drive. Improved property includes a survey with topo layout, septic system, Birch Bay Water and Sewer with meter, and water access via four spigots. Nestled among majestic Fir and Cedar trees, the property offers a gentle slope and optimal western sun exposure. Part of a 32-parcel stretch held by Washington States DNR until 2070, it promises stability under RCW 79.13. Enjoy potential filtered water views for your future build. A sustainable and serene haven awaits you.

Welcome to this charming newly refreshed 1910 home! This is a 2+ bedroom home loaded with windows and light. Large kitchen with lots of cabinets for storage. Spacious bathroom has large tiled shower. Curl up in your living room next to cozy gas free standing stove. Peaceful private treed setting with mature landscaping and mostly fenced yard for your ultimate enjoyment. Huge 480sf detached shop for parking or workshop. Close to town yet feels like living in the country. Gas furnace and hot water heater is brand new this year. This home is not in the flood zone. Don't miss seeing this home today.

Get ready to live like youre on vacation in this charming 2 bed, 1.75 bath, Sudden Valley Gate 2 condo with wooded & golf course views! Enjoy vaulted ceilings for an airy feel, a free standing pellet stove for an extra cozy touch and hard surface floors throughout - not a stitch of carpet. Venture through your dining area slider out onto your lovely, private-feeling covered deck to have your morning coffee, or relax in your sizable primary suite. With plenty of storage, plus walking distance to nearly all of Sudden Valleys amenities including the professional 18-hole golf course, two outdoor pools, fitness center, beaches, restaurants and more, this perfectly located, well-maintained condo is one youll definitely want to see!

The value in this home is the 1/25th share in Calmor Cove Club on Lake Samish, the Northwest's premier original waterski park. Get the boat in the water! Ideal, remarkable location just 5 min off I-5, South Lake Samish exit. View of lake and mountains. New TPO roof, all updated electric, plumbing rehab 2024. So many recreational options! Private dock space available. Community water Lake Samish surface water. Home in need of updating. 2 BR, 1 full BA. Single space carport w/shed. Wood fireplace/stove. Full time or second home, all ages - no rentals. Low dues and low taxes! Welcome to Lake Samish!

Hobby farm life you've been looking for! Well-maintained 2, 000+ sq ft home w/bonus room on over an acre in Lynden SD. Long driveway w/plenty of parking & RV 50-amp hookup welcomes you to this lovely home w/thoughtful fenced areas & several outbuildings backing to tree-lined boundary. All 3 bedrooms inc owner's suite are on main floor w/bonus room upstairs. Vaulted living room, great size dining & eat-in kitchen all flooded w/natural light. Warm & cozy spacious kitchen has brand new gas stove & dishwasher. Owner's suite w/full ensuite bath inc jetted tub & walk-in closet also boasts great views of expansive yard. Enjoy ample shelving in the garage, perfect for all of your projects & storage. Gorgeous sunrise/sunset views to top it all off!

Discover this beautiful home, filled with warmth and charm, in the desirable Northern Heights neighborhood. Not in an HOA and on the market for the first time! Featuring three bedrooms plus an office, vaulted ceilings, tons of natural light, gorgeous hardwood floors, and a 3 car garage. Single owner has lovingly cared for the home and gardens; rosebushes, blueberries bushes, mature landscaping and a greenhouse or shed await you at this turnkey home. Property backs up to an undevelopable wooded area, enjoy the unrivaled privacy and peacefulness of nature from your back deck, while still having easy access to everything that Bellingham has to offer! Walking distance to Northern Heights Elementary, Squalicum Highschool, and a WTA Bus Route.

Affordable rambler on good size lot backing to school in great location - ready for new owners looking for some sweat equity opportunities. Would make a great flip for a savvy investor or bring your vision & your pinterest board to dive into cosmetic updates. Oak hdwd flooring throughout most of home (hiding under living rm carpet too). 4 bd, 1 3/4 bath with good size living room open to dining off kitchen. Utility room is a great size & has an albeit unique 3/4 bath included. Fully fenced spacious backyard & extra parking, plenty of room to garden, play, park toys & more. Bring your imagination & tools - room to earn equity!

Ideal location in the fabulous Ridgemont neighborhood!
